import SVGImg1 from '../../images/svg-1.svg';
import SVGImg2 from '../../images/svg-12.svg';

export const homeObjOne = {
    id: 'about',
    lightBg: true,
    lightText: false,
    lightTextDesc: false,
    topLine: 'About me',
    headLine: 'Create the things dont just imagine.',
    description: "I enjoy building everything from small business sites to rich interactive web apps. If you are a business seeking a web presence or an employer looking to hire, you can get in touch with me here.",
    buttonLabel: 'Contact me',
    imgStart: false,
    img: SVGImg1,
    alt: 'Car',
    dark: false,
    primary: false,
    darkText: true,
    link: "https://www.linkedin.com/in/tanishqbiswas"
}; 

export const homeObjTwo = {
    id: 'experience',
    lightBg: true,
    lightText: false,
    lightTextDesc: false,
    topLine: 'Add on',
    headLine: 'Experienced in Graphic and UI Designing',
    description: 'Worked with 15+ Organization and succesfully executed 60+ projects as an UI and Graphic Designer as a Freelancer.',
    buttonLabel: 'Portfolio',
    imgStart: true,
    img: SVGImg2,
    alt: 'Car',
    dark: false,
    primary: false,
    darkText: true,
    link: "https://dribbble.com/tanishqbiswas"
};
